    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Catto Bellovaci <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>domo Segusiavo equiti <lb n="3"/>alae Maced<expan><ex>o</ex><abbr>nicae</abbr></expan> <lb n="4"/>ex testamento <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> Cornelius <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>iti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> Fronto faciundum <lb n="6"/>quravit <note>sic</note> idemque probavit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Cattus bislang nur in Gallien belegt gewesen (ILTG 445; CIL XIII 3305). Erster Beleg für Bellovacus als Cognomen. Y: Seit 15 n. Chr. provincia inermis. (B): AE 1982, 0856 bietet irrtuümlicherweise Maced(o)nicae) in Z. 3.</p>
            </div>
